songs.title: Dada
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Dada
Dada
Dada

[Hook (x2)]
Kaun badle mera irada
Sada main nibhaoon karke waada (dada)
Kaun mere se zyada
Jo hai mera hai diya khuda ka (dada)

[Verse 1]
Dushmann kamzor
Peeth piche log karein shor
Tactic force, mera picha kare leke Infrared Scope
Mere picha kare roz
Mukhbar chup kar bane dost
Bahar flow karu rap jaise chlau main machine gun do
Par main aadmi ek mujhe army takeover karne lage
Mere piche mujhe chain ik pal na
Jeeni raat jaise subah ho nikalna
Ye mera irada, dada

[Hook (x4)]
Kaun badle mera irada
Sada main nibhaoon karke waada (dada)
Kaun mere se zyada
Jo hai mera hai diya khuda ka (dada)

[Bridge]
Dada (uh)
Dada
Dada (huh)

[Hook (x2)]
Kaun badle mera irada
Sada main nibhaoon karke waada (dada)
Kaun mere se zyada
Jo hai mera hai diya khuda ka (dada)

[Verse 2]
Dushmann darpok
Mere todh ka ni jodh (dada)
Machine gun flow
Chalau ek goli mere vairi mare do
Mere haath, tez karu vaar
Tez tere sawalon ka dunga main jawaab
Tez meri team, tez meri beat mein bass
Meri dadagiri chale kisi bhi des mein (dada)

[Hook (x4)]
Kaun badle mera irada
Sada main nibhaoon karke wada (dada)
Kaun mere se zyada
Jo hai mera hai diya khuda ka (dada)

[Outro]
Dada
Dada
Dada
